title: Winning numbers drawn in 'Gimme 5' game
maintext:
CONCORD, N.H. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Monday evening’s drawing of the “Gimme 5” game were:
01-05-08-12-31
(one, five, eight, twelve, thirty-one)
